                <h4 class="u-text u-text-grey-70 u-text-36">
                  <span style="font-weight: 700;"> End to end client experience</span>
                  <br> AllbizHub is a secure end-to-end client experience platform for small businesses that enables you to Pitch Premium Proposals, Convert those to quotes and invoices, &nbsp;Manage the project, and Get Credit from a single page.<br>Contact more customers, stay organised, and get paid faster.
                </h4>
                <h5 class="u-text u-text-grey-70 u-text-37">
                  <span style="font-weight: 700;">What are the terms of the AllbizHub contract?</span>
                  <br>AllbizHub is available on a month-to-month basis with automatic renewal. You can choose between paying annually, which saves you over 10%, and paying month to month.
                </h5>
                <h4 class="u-text u-text-grey-70 u-text-38">
                  <span style="font-weight: 700;"> Can I upgrade at any time?</span>
                  <br>Users who are on the free plan can upgrade to the base plan plus at any time. Our base plan is always $99 per month, with 10 users included, and extra users can be added for AUD&nbsp;$9.90 per month. Select extra users from the subscription drop-down menu on your dashboard. If you require additional emails per month or document storage contact support or checkout the support hub pricing.&nbsp;
                </h4>
                <h4 class="u-text u-text-grey-70 u-text-39">
                  <span style="font-weight: 700;"></span>
                  <span style="font-weight: 700;">What happens if I upgrade within my paid-in-full contract term?</span>
                  <br>Don't worry, we'll prorate the difference over the course of your subscription.
                </h4>
                <h4 class="u-text u-text-grey-70 u-text-40">
                  <span style="font-weight: 700;">Do I have to use all of the software's features and tools?</span>
                  <br>Yes, you have full access to all services with some limitations on the number of emails you can send each month and the amount of data you can save. You may always upgrade these, and we guarantee that any add-ons will keep us competitive.
                </h4>
                <h4 class="u-text u-text-grey-70 u-text-41">
                  <span style="font-weight: 700;"></span>
                  <span style="font-weight: 700;">What happens if I upgrade within my paid-in-full contract term?</span>
                  <br>Don't worry, we'll prorate the difference over the course of your subscription.
                </h4>
                <h6 class="u-custom-font u-text u-text-font u-text-grey-70 u-text-42">
                  <span style="font-weight: 700;"></span>When will I be able to use AllbizHub? Is it necessary for me to download the software?<br>
                  <span style="font-weight: 400;">AllbizHub does not require installation because it is a cloud-based solution.&nbsp;Your own subdomain, such as yourbusiness.allbizhub.com, will be created instantly. The email address you used to signup determines your AllbizHub login profile.. By heading to your userprofile on the dashboard, you can create your own unique password and username, which you can change at any point.</span>
                </h6>
                <h4 class="u-text u-text-grey-70 u-text-43">
                  <span style="font-weight: 700;">What is the best browser to use for AllbizHub?</span>
                  <br>AllbizHub is best viewed on Chrome, but it can also be viewed in Firefox and Safari.&nbsp;
                </h4>
                <h4 class="u-text u-text-grey-70 u-text-44">
                  <span style="font-style: normal;">
                    <span style="font-weight: 700;">Is there a charge for onboarding?</span>
                    <br>No, we offer free live chat support seven days a week to assist you in getting started. If you need a specialist to onboard your system, we can connect you with a marketplace of service providers.
                  </span>
                </h4>
                <h4 class="u-text u-text-grey-70 u-text-45">
                  <span style="font-weight: 700;">How long does it take to create an AllbizHub account?</span>
                  <br>You will instantly be logged in and able to utilise AllbizHub following your purchase. The Getting started guide&nbsp;you in the setup and&nbsp;we'll assist you in setting the most crucial features. We also offer various template setups for industries or business logic.
                </h4>
                <h4 class="u-text u-text-grey-70 u-text-46">
                  <span style="font-weight: 700;">Can I utilise all features in my AllbizHub account as a free user?</span>
                  <br>Absolutely. There are certain limitations on the amount of accounts, emails, and data storage, but all services are available on the free plan except for the website and landing page builder.Don't worry, we'll prorate the difference over the course of your subscription.
                </h4>
